from solution import Solution
# simple test harness
sol = Solution()
cases = [
    ("dart", 3, "tdar"),
    ("aaa", 1, "aaa"),
    ("abc", 2, "cab"),
    ("z", 10000, "z"),
    ("abcd", 4, "abcd"),
    ("abcd", 5, "bcda"),
]
failed = []
for s,k,exp in cases:
    out = sol.getEncryptedString(s,k)
    ok = out == exp
    print(f"s={s!r} k={k} => out={out!r} expected={exp!r} {"OK" if ok else "FAIL"}")
    if not ok:
        failed.append((s,k,out,exp))
print("FAILED:", failed)
